      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-04-19T00:20:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you think something like this would also work?\n\n   ApplyLazyInheritedAttribute(*);\n\n   if (attrs.fColor.isValid()) {\n     // local color attribute -\u003e update all currentColor dependents\n     if (fPresentationContext-\u003efInherited.fFill-\u003etype() \u003d\u003d SkSVGPaint::Type::kCurrentColor) {\n       applySVGPaint(...)\n     }\n     ...\n   }",
